Name: Jinzhou Skewers
AttributesDescription: Increases ATK of all Resonators in the team by 100, lasting for 15m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: Skewers that have become a favorite for everyone in Jinzhou and must-have on the menu of every restaurant in Jinzhou. But each restaurant has its own secret recipe. "Come to my place, my skewers are the real deal!"
